Research Objectives:\n\n1. Determination of Optimal Conditions for Rapid and Quantitative Fluoride Estimation Using Marigold Flower Extract\n\nThis study aims to establish the ideal parameters for a swift and accurate spectrophotometric method of fluoride quantification utilizing marigold flower extract. The optimization process will involve investigating various factors such as pH, temperature, reaction time, and reagent concentrations to ensure maximum sensitivity and reliability of the assay.\n\n2